@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Authentication (Login & Register)
actor User
participant "UI (LoginActivity/RegisterActivity)" as UI
participant "AuthService" as ViewModel
participant "FirebaseAuth" as Auth
participant "Google SignIn API" as Google

== Register ==
User -> UI : Enter Email & Password, click Register
UI -> ViewModel : register(email, password)
ViewModel -> Auth : createUserWithEmailAndPassword()
activate Auth
Auth --> ViewModel : AuthResult (Success/Failure)
deactivate Auth
ViewModel --> UI : Update State (Success/Error)
UI --> User : Show message / Navigate to Login

== Login with Email ==
User -> UI : Enter Email & Password, click Login
UI -> ViewModel : login(email, password)
ViewModel -> Auth : signInWithEmailAndPassword()
activate Auth
Auth --> ViewModel : AuthResult
deactivate Auth
ViewModel --> UI : Update State
UI --> User : Navigate to Home / Show Error

== Login with Google ==
User -> UI : Click Login with Google
UI -> Google : request SignIn Intent
activate Google
Google --> UI : return Intent
deactivate Google
UI -> User : Show Google Account Picker
User --> UI : Select Account
UI -> Google : getSignedInAccount()
activate Google
Google --> UI : return idToken
deactivate Google
UI -> ViewModel : loginWithGoogle(idToken)
ViewModel -> Auth : signInWithCredential(credential)
activate Auth
Auth --> ViewModel : AuthResult
deactivate Auth
ViewModel --> UI : Update State
UI --> User : Navigate to Home / Show Error

== Logout ==
User -> UI : Click Logout
UI -> ViewModel : logout()
ViewModel -> Auth : signOut()
Auth --> ViewModel : Success
ViewModel --> UI : Clear Session
UI --> User : Navigate to Login Screen
@enduml
